  "texts": [
    "The videos have high-definition (720P) or ultra-high-definition (1080 P) resolutions.",
    "Among these videos, one thousand videos come with per-frame annotations, including object bounding box positions, object categories, and tracking IDs.",
    "These annotations cover a total of 12 categories related to driving and road-related objects.What sets D²-City apart from similar datasets is its data collection from various cities in China, encompassing diverse weather conditions, road types, and traffic scenarios, including highly complex and diverse traffic scenes.",
    "D²-City also participated in the Object Detection Transfer Learning Challenge, where participants were required to train object detection models using the BDD100K dataset collected in the United States and apply them to the D²-City dataset from China.",
    "The dataset may contain data captured under rare or challenging conditions such as low light, rainy/foggy weather, and congested roads."
  ],
